		"description": {
			"value": "<p>Wondrous Item - Rare</p><br><p><em>Typically [[/r 1d4+4]] Beads of Force are found together. Each bead is a small black sphere, Â¾ inch in diameter, weighing 1 ounce.</em></p><br><p><br /></p><br><p><strong>Action</strong> - 10 ft Radius (60 ft.)</p><br><p><strong>[[/save DEX 15]]{Dexterity Save (DC 15)}</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> Target takes [[/damage 5d4 force]] damage and, if completely within the area, is trapped inside a transparent force sphere for 1 minute.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> Half damage, target is pushed outside the sphere's boundary.</p></li></ul><p><br /></p><br><p><strong>Properties</strong></p><ul><li><p>Only breathable air can pass through its walls; no attacks or other effects can pass through.</p></li><li><p>A trapped creature may take a Utilize action to push against the wall, moving the sphere up to half its Speed.</p></li><li><p>The sphere can be picked up and always weighs 1 pound, regardless of contents.</p></li></ul>",
